Miss Chan，我点过两次了！
Miss Chan, I've been called twice!

105
00:07:43,625 --> 00:07:45,208
呀，真的吗？
Oops!

106
00:07:45,917 --> 00:07:48,417
校长早晨！
Good morning, sir!

107
