Be good,

477
00:40:55,208 --> 00:40:58,667
跟师傅学习，光宗耀祖！
learn with the master and honour the ancestors.

478
00:41:05,625 --> 00:41:10,083
妈妈在长洲找了间酒楼摆拜师宴
In honour of my master, mother throws a banquet.

479
00:41:11,000 --> 00:41:14,583
因为我是师傅最后一个入室弟子
As I am the last disciple of the master…

480
00:41:14,750 --> 00:41:18,125
